{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/post/dragons-crown-game-yang-dicela-dan-dipuja/","result":{"data":{"wordpressPost":{"title":"Dragon&#8217;s Crown: Game yang Dicela dan Dipuja","content":"<p>Dragon’s Crown adalah <em>game</em> yang menimbulkan polarisasi di antara penggemar <em>video game</em>. Perbedaan pendapat yang ada sama kuatnya. Sebagian memuji IP ini, sementara sisanya mencela. Semua dengan pendapat dan argumentasi mereka masing-masing. Tapi terlepas dari polarisasi tersebut, Dragon’s Crown merupakan sebuah karya seni <em>video game</em> yang ‘berfungsi secara tepat jika berada di segmen pasar yang sesuai’.</p>\n<p>Untuk penulis sendiri, Dragon’s Crown adalah sebuah keberanian desain. <em>Game</em> ini mengambil <em>gameplay</em> <em>2D Side-Scrolling Beat ‘Em Up Role-Playing Game.</em> Ini adalah genre yang semakin ditinggalkan oleh banyak <em>developer video games</em> dengan alasan kalau pasarnya sudah habis digerus oleh <em>game</em> 3D.</p>\n<p>“2D <em>Side-Scrolling is dead</em>”, kata mereka. Dan pada satu titik, <em>gamers</em> mungkin harus percaya. Selama puluhan tahun ke belakang, sangat sedikit <em>game</em> serupa atau 2D<em> Side-Scrolling</em> yang dibuat oleh <em>developers</em>. Terbaru mungkin Cuphead? <em>Game</em> itu tergolong sukses di pasaran dan <em>reviews</em>. Jadi mengatakan genre 2D <em>Side-Scrolling</em> sudah mati atau tidak akan sukses merupakan sebuah kebodohan.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_44794\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-44794\" data-attachment-id=\"44794\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/dragons-crown-game-yang-dicela-dan-dipuja/attachment/dcrown1/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/dcrown1.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Cuphead menggunakan genre yang mirip dengan Dragon’s Crown (Sumber gambar: gamespot.com)\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Cuphead menggunakan genre yang mirip dengan Dragon’s Crown (Sumber gambar: gamespot.com)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/dcrown1-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/dcrown1.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-44794\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/dcrown1.jpg\" alt=\"Cuphead menggunakan genre yang mirip dengan Dragon’s Crown (Sumber gambar: gamespot.com)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/dcrown1.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/dcrown1-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-44794\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Cuphead menggunakan genre yang mirip dengan Dragon’s Crown (Sumber gambar: gamespot.com)</p></div>\n<p><em>Developer</em> Dragon’s Crown adalah Vanillaware Ltd. <em>Game </em>keluaran Vanillaware sebelumnya seperti Odin Sphere, GrimGrimoire atau Muramasa: The Demon Blade merupakan contoh bagaimana sebuah <em>game </em>bernuansa dua dimensi dengan sentuhan elemen RPG klasik yang seru dan menantang bisa sukses. Selain <em>gameplay side-scrolling</em> yang diadopsi oleh <em>game</em> Vanillaware ini, <em>artwork game</em> yang unik merupakan ciri khas lain dari Vanillaware.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_44795\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-44795\" data-attachment-id=\"44795\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/dragons-crown-game-yang-dicela-dan-dipuja/attachment/dcrown2/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/dcrown2.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Odin Sphere (Sumber gambar: pixelperfectgaming.com)\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Odin Sphere (Sumber gambar: pixelperfectgaming.com)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/dcrown2-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/dcrown2.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-44795\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/dcrown2.jpg\" alt=\"Odin Sphere (Sumber gambar: pixelperfectgaming.com)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/dcrown2.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/dcrown2-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-44795\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Odin Sphere (Sumber gambar: pixelperfectgaming.com)</p></div>\n<p>Untuk yang sudah pernah atau familiar dengan<em> games</em> buatan Vanillaware, Dragon’s Crown menggunakan pola <em>gameplay</em> yang mirip dengan<em> game</em> sebelumnya. Dengan pergerakan dua dimensi kiri ke kanan ala <em>game beat ‘em up</em> “Bare Knuckle” (<em>game Mega Drive</em>) dengan konsep ala RPG seperti “Guardian Heroes” (game klasik keren Sega Saturn), Dragon’s Crown memberikan sebuah keseruan game baku gebuk namun dengan mekanisme upgrade/system/magic/item managements layaknya sebuah <a href=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/final-fantasy-vii-bukan-final-fantasy-yang-terbaik-tapi-paling-fenomenal/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">game RPG seperti misalnya Final Fantasy VII</a>. Tentu tidak sedalam RPG normal namun cukup menarik dan menambah keseruan bermain.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_44796\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-44796\" data-attachment-id=\"44796\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/dragons-crown-game-yang-dicela-dan-dipuja/attachment/dcrown3/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/dcrown3.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Tampilan in-game Dragon’s Crown (Sumber gambar: comicbook.com)\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Tampilan in-game Dragon’s Crown (Sumber gambar: comicbook.com)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/dcrown3-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/dcrown3.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-44796\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/dcrown3.jpg\" alt=\"Tampilan in-game Dragon’s Crown (Sumber gambar: comicbook.com)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/dcrown3.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/dcrown3-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-44796\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Tampilan in-game Dragon’s Crown (Sumber gambar: comicbook.com)</p></div>\n<p>Grafis dari Dragon’s Crown dibuat dengan metode ‘hand-drawn’ alias digambar dengan tangan. Tidak menggunakan metode modern polygonal graphic seperti di kebanyakan game modern. Hal ini menjadikan Dragon’s Crown memiliki tampilan cemerlang dan klasik. Warna-warna lukisan tangan yang dihasilkan team dibawah panduan sutradara George Kamitani (yang juga merupakan Boss alias Presiden Vanillaware Ltd.) bagaikan sebuah anime yang hidup. Sangat indah. Fans games dari Vanillaware pasti mengerti apa yang saya maksudkan.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_44797\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-44797\" data-attachment-id=\"44797\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/dragons-crown-game-yang-dicela-dan-dipuja/attachment/dcrown4/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/dcrown4.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Gameplay ketat dengan grafik cakep (Sumber gambar: pushsquare.com)\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Gameplay ketat dengan grafik cakep (Sumber gambar: pushsquare.com)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/dcrown4-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/dcrown4.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-44797\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/dcrown4.jpg\" alt=\"Gameplay ketat dengan grafik cakep (Sumber gambar: pushsquare.com)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/dcrown4.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/dcrown4-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-44797\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Gameplay ketat dengan grafik cakep (Sumber gambar: pushsquare.com)</p></div>\n<p>Gameplay khas <em>game beat ‘em up</em>. Grafis ala anime. Gimana dengan <em>storyline</em> dari Dragon’s Crown. Mengambil setting Kingdom of Hydeland, lokasi yang sama seperti game Vanillaware lainnya, yaitu GrimGrimoire dan Odin Sphere. Tapi tentu berada dalam <em>timeline</em> serta areal berbeda dari kedua judul tadi. Plot utamanya tentang perjalanan pencarian &#8220;relic&#8221;, benda berkekuatan magis kuno “Dragon’s Crown” oleh sekelompok petualangan. Masing-masing dari mereka memiliki kemampuan berbeda yang akan berguna sepanjang perjalanan.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_44798\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-44798\" data-attachment-id=\"44798\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/dragons-crown-game-yang-dicela-dan-dipuja/attachment/dcrown5/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/dcrown5.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Karakter atau Job Class di Dragon’s Crown (Sumber gambar: dragons-crown.wikia.com)\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Karakter atau Job Class di Dragon’s Crown (Sumber gambar: dragons-crown.wikia.com)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/dcrown5-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/dcrown5.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-44798\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/dcrown5.jpg\" alt=\"Karakter atau Job Class di Dragon’s Crown (Sumber gambar: dragons-crown.wikia.com)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/dcrown5.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/dcrown5-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-44798\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Karakter atau Job Class di Dragon’s Crown (Sumber gambar: dragons-crown.wikia.com)</p></div>\n<p>Karakter-karakter ini adalah:</p>\n<p><strong>Amazon.</strong> Wanita berkekuatan besar dengan kemampuan menggunakan senjata yang memerlukan dua tangan. Lincah dan mematikan.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_44799\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-44799\" data-attachment-id=\"44799\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/dragons-crown-game-yang-dicela-dan-dipuja/attachment/dcrown6/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/dcrown6.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Amazon (Sumber gambar: dragons-crown.wikia.com)\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Amazon (Sumber gambar: dragons-crown.wikia.com)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/dcrown6-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/dcrown6.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-44799\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/dcrown6.jpg\" alt=\"Amazon (Sumber gambar: dragons-crown.wikia.com)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/dcrown6.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/dcrown6-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-44799\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Amazon (Sumber gambar: dragons-crown.wikia.com)</p></div>\n<p><strong>Dwarf.</strong> Petarung kuat berotot, sehingga memungkinkan penggunaan dua senjata berbeda di setiap lengan. Sanggup mengangkat dan melempar musuh yang lebih besar dan berat.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_44800\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-44800\" data-attachment-id=\"44800\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/dragons-crown-game-yang-dicela-dan-dipuja/attachment/dcrown7/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/dcrown7.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Dwarf (Sumber gambar: destructoid.com)\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Dwarf (Sumber gambar: destructoid.com)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/dcrown7-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/dcrown7.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-44800\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/dcrown7.jpg\" alt=\"Dwarf (Sumber gambar: destructoid.com)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/dcrown7.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/dcrown7-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-44800\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Dwarf (Sumber gambar: destructoid.com)</p></div>\n<p><strong>Elf.</strong> Bertubuh langsing dan ahli menggunakan busur serta panah dibandingkan ras lainnya. Punya penampilan yang terlihat muda walau usia jauh lebih tua dari yang terlihat.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_44801\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-44801\" data-attachment-id=\"44801\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/dragons-crown-game-yang-dicela-dan-dipuja/attachment/dcrown8/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/dcrown8.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Elf (Sumber gambar: dragons-crown.wikia.com)\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Elf (Sumber gambar: dragons-crown.wikia.com)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/dcrown8-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/dcrown8.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-44801\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/dcrown8.jpg\" alt=\"Elf (Sumber gambar: dragons-crown.wikia.com)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/dcrown8.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/dcrown8-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-44801\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Elf (Sumber gambar: dragons-crown.wikia.com)</p></div>\n<p><strong>Fighter.</strong> Ahli bertempur dengan kekuatan besar, armor serta perisai kokoh. Walau memiliki kekuatan defensif yang tangguh namun juga dapat menyerang dengan senjata yang ada di tangan.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_44802\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-44802\" data-attachment-id=\"44802\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/dragons-crown-game-yang-dicela-dan-dipuja/attachment/dcrown9/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/dcrown9.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Fighter (Sumber gambar: egmnow.com)\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Fighter (Sumber gambar: egmnow.com)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/dcrown9-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/dcrown9.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-44802\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/dcrown9.jpg\" alt=\"Fighter (Sumber gambar: egmnow.com)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/dcrown9.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/dcrown9-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-44802\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Fighter (Sumber gambar: egmnow.com)</p></div>\n<p><strong>Sorceress.</strong> Wanita menawan dengan keahlian <em>dark magic</em>. Termasuk kelas <em>support</em> yang punya skill berguna: bisa menciptakan makanan lezat, mengendalikan tengkorak/<em>undead</em> atau mengubah musuh menjadi kodok. Memiliki tubuh yang tidak terlalu kuat namun punya <em>skill magic</em> yang hebat.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_44803\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-44803\" data-attachment-id=\"44803\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/dragons-crown-game-yang-dicela-dan-dipuja/attachment/dcrown10/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/dcrown10.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Sorceress (Sumber gambar: YouTube)\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Sorceress (Sumber gambar: YouTube)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/dcrown10-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/dcrown10.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-44803\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/dcrown10.jpg\" alt=\"Sorceress (Sumber gambar: YouTube)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/dcrown10.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/dcrown10-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-44803\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sorceress (Sumber gambar: YouTube)</p></div>\n<p><strong>Wizard.</strong> Punya keahlian mirip Sorceress namun dengan gender pria. Kemampuan sihir dikatakan sama bagusnya dengan Sorceress.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_44804\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-44804\" data-attachment-id=\"44804\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/dragons-crown-game-yang-dicela-dan-dipuja/attachment/dcrown11/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/dcrown11.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Wizard (Sumber gambar: dualshockers.com)\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Wizard (Sumber gambar: dualshockers.com)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/dcrown11-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/dcrown11.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-44804\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/dcrown11.jpg\" alt=\"Wizard (Sumber gambar: dualshockers.com)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/dcrown11.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/dcrown11-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-44804\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Wizard (Sumber gambar: dualshockers.com)</p></div>\n<p>Dragon’s Crown mendapatkan celaan seperti misalnya dari Kotaku karena desain karakter yang dianggap terlalu ‘<em>over the top</em>’ (terutama oleh kelompok <em>non gamers</em> serta <em>feminists</em>). Karakter Sorceress dan Amazon misalnya; karakter ini dianggap terlalu seksi sehingga mereka mencoba memaksa Vanillaware melakukan perubahan desain.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_44805\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-44805\" data-attachment-id=\"44805\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/dragons-crown-game-yang-dicela-dan-dipuja/attachment/dcrown12/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/dcrown12.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Desain George Kamitani dari Vanillaware (Sumber gambar: knowyourmeme.com)\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Desain George Kamitani dari Vanillaware (Sumber gambar: knowyourmeme.com)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/dcrown12-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/dcrown12.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-44805\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/dcrown12.jpg\" alt=\"Desain George Kamitani dari Vanillaware (Sumber gambar: knowyourmeme.com)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/dcrown12.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/dcrown12-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-44805\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Desain George Kamitani dari Vanillaware (Sumber gambar: knowyourmeme.com)</p></div>\n<p>Namun George Kamitani, sebagai bagian desainer karakter Dragon’s Crown memberikan argumen kalau desain mereka ditujukan agar karakter <em>game</em> ini ‘berbeda dari <em>game</em> lainnya’. Tadinya mereka menggunakan desain ala “Dungeons and Dragons” dengan sentuhan inspirasi dunia J.R.R. Tolkien. Namun saat sudah jadi, karakter-karakter ini terlihat biasa-biasa saja sehingga Kamitani dan timnya memutuskan untuk melakukan perubahan desain secara radikal dan ‘<em>exaggerate</em>’ alias berlebihan dengan spirit khas anime.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_44806\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-44806\" data-attachment-id=\"44806\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/dragons-crown-game-yang-dicela-dan-dipuja/attachment/dcrown13/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/dcrown13.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"George Kamitani dari Vanillaware (Sumber gambar: dragons-crown.wikia.com)\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;George Kamitani dari Vanillaware (Sumber gambar: dragons-crown.wikia.com)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/dcrown13-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/dcrown13.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-44806\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/dcrown13.jpg\" alt=\"George Kamitani dari Vanillaware (Sumber gambar: dragons-crown.wikia.com)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/dcrown13.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/dcrown13-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-44806\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">George Kamitani dari Vanillaware (Sumber gambar: dragons-crown.wikia.com)</p></div>\n<p>Walau menyisakan omelan bagi mereka yang tidak menyukai desain karakter di Dragon’s Crown, nyatanya <em>game</em> ini sukses di pasaran. <em>Metacritic</em> memberikan skor 82/100 untuk versi PlayStation 3 dan 78/100 untuk PlayStation Vita. Famitsu memberi nilai 34/40 dan Joystiq dengan 4 ½ bintang dari 5. Sementara secara sales, Dragon’s Crown sudah terjual di angka 940.000 unit. Cukup meyakinkan!</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_44807\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-44807\" data-attachment-id=\"44807\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/dragons-crown-game-yang-dicela-dan-dipuja/attachment/dcrown14/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/dcrown14.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Dicela dan dipuja gamers dunia (Sumber gambar: gematsu.com)\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Dicela dan dipuja gamers dunia (Sumber gambar: gematsu.com)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/dcrown14-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/dcrown14.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-44807\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/dcrown14.jpg\" alt=\"Dicela dan dipuja gamers dunia (Sumber gambar: gematsu.com)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/dcrown14.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/dcrown14-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-44807\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Dicela dan dipuja gamers dunia (Sumber gambar: gematsu.com)</p></div>\n<p>Terkini,<em> game</em> Dragon’s Crown mendapatkan ‘<em>make over</em>’ alias versi <em>Remastered</em> untuk PlayStation 4. Diberi judul “Dragon’s Crown Pro”, <em>game</em> ini memiliki tampilan grafis definisi tinggi hingga resolusi 4K, <em>soundtrack live orchestra</em>, pilihan bahasa Inggris atau Jepang dan semua DLC yang dulu dijual terpisah. <em>Game</em> ini sudah rilis di Jepang pada February 2018 dan versi Amerika akan menyusul di Mei 2018.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><iframe src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/1yaHsStVDNM\" width=\"560\" height=\"315\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></p>\n<p>Sudah pernah main Dragon’s Crown di PS3? Atau pengen coba yang versi Pro? Punya opini lain tentang <em>game</em> keren ini? Tag saya di komentar kalian, ya!</p>\n"}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"id":"9e7ee38f-9fbe-55ea-b740-e30349bfd604"}}}